\ldblquote So this year, we train harder than ever before. \'85 Okay, let\rquote s go and put our new theories into practice!\rdblquote  Wood shouted, seizing his broomstick and leading the way out of the locker rooms. Stiff-legged and still yawning, his team followed.\par
