\ldblquote What\rquote s that funny clicking noise?\rdblquote  called Fred as they hurtled around the corner.\par
Harry looked into the stands. Colin was sitting in one of the highest seats, his camera raised, taking picture after picture, the sound strangely magnified in the deserted stadium.\par
\ldblquote Look this way, Harry! This way!\rdblquote  he cried shrilly.\par
\ldblquote Who\rquote s that?\rdblquote  said Fred.\par
\ldblquote No idea,\rdblquote  Harry lied, putting on a spurt of speed that took him as far away as possible from Colin.\par
