Professor Binns paused again, pursing his lips, looking like a wrinkled old tortoise.\par
\ldblquote Reliable historical sources tell us this much,\rdblquote  he said. \ldblquote But these honest facts have been obscured by the fanciful legend of the Chamber of Secrets. The story goes that Slytherin had built a hidden chamber in the castle, of which the other founders knew nothing.\par
