\pard\nowidctlpar\fi284\qj\lang1033 Harry went to bed before anyone else in his dormitory that night. This was partly because he didn\rquote t think he could stand Fred and George singing, \ldblquote His eyes are as green as a fresh pickled toad\rdblquote  one more time, and partly because he wanted to examine Riddle\rquote s diary again, and knew that Ron thought he was wasting his time.\par
