There was a knock on the office door.\par
\ldblquote Enter,\rdblquote  said the old wizard in a feeble voice.\par
A boy of about sixteen entered, taking off his pointed hat. A sil\-ver prefect\rquote s badge was glinting on his chest. He was much taller than Harry, but he, too, had jet-black hair.\par
